metadata.name: OSHUN
metadata.description:
Before the emergence of the ROYAL NIGER COMPANY (Known as Nigeria today), was the existence of the ORISHAS who were created by the Supreme creator Olódùmarè.
Each piece in this collection, focuses on the Yoruba goddess OSHUN who is known for femininity, beauty, and fertility, whilst
paying homage to African mythology, the Yoruba religion, and the RICH cultural history of South Western Nigeria.
